claim: José María Chacón was responsible for signing the yearbook in 1783.
premise_source_doc_sentence: He was responsible for signing the Cedula of Population in 1783  (  which led to extensive French immigration to Trinidad  )  , founded the city of San Fernando in 1784 and surrendered the island of Trinidad to a British fleet under the command of Sir Ralph Abercromby in 1797 .
